  "detailHtml": "<p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"></p><h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">【商品介绍与套餐选择】</span></h3><ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"9\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本产品提供极度细分与弹性的算力配置，请根据您的剧集产量与更新频率进行选择：</span></p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,5\" data-index-in-node=\"3\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,1\" data-index-in-node=\"3\">【服务类别选择】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">【全新独立账号】</strong>：发货为您提供含对应等级会员的全新海外独立账号，资产独享，纯净防封。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">【自有账号代充】</strong>：请提供您的 Hailuo 注册邮箱，为您官方网关纯净直充升级，无缝保留您的历史角色提示词与分镜资产。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">【积分代充 (Credits)】</strong>：<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"17\">爆肝推剧必备。</strong>&nbsp;专为订阅额度耗尽的重度操盘手准备，直充生图/视频美元积分，瞬间拉满弹药库。</span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,2,0\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,5\" data-index-in-node=\"3\" style=\"white-space: normal;\">【美元积分加油包 (随充随用)】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">从 <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"2\">$5刀 (600积分)</strong> 的轻量补给，到 <strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"22\">$300刀 (40000积分)</strong> 的工业级弹药库，共 8 个档位任选。随时为您的超级大片注入极速渲染动力</span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,6,0,0\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,3\" data-index-in-node=\"3\" style=\"white-space: normal;\">【会员规格详解 (包月制)】</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Standard / Pro 会员</strong>：<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"18\">个人创作者起号优选。</strong> 满足日常短视频更新、自媒体小说推文的连贯画面需求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Master / Ultra 会员&nbsp; 中型工作室主力</strong>：<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"29\">高频叙事引擎。</strong> 算力与并发数大幅跃升，完美应对多部 AI 短剧同时开机的并发需求，显著缩短成片周期。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Max 顶配会员&nbsp; 工业级天花板</strong>：<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,0,4,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"19\">无情的流量印钞机。</strong> 专为顶尖出海泛娱乐矩阵、4A 级广告公司打造。无视一切算力瓶颈，以最高优先级队列独享海螺顶配算力。</span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,2,0,0\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;2. 虚拟产品，发货/充值成功后，除质量问题外，不支持退换请谅解。介意勿拍。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3.&nbsp;<strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">官网登录地址：</strong><strong data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><response-element class=\"\" ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\"><link-block _nghost-ng-c4076580434=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><a _ngcontent-ng-c4076580434=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" externallink=\"\" _nghost-ng-c970244732=\"\" jslog=\"197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_70c77c6657046547&quot;,&quot;c_2b21d711a5437fb8&quot;,null,&quot;rc_15b6b50cb3a2f7db&quot;,null,null,&quot;zh&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]\" href=\"https://hailuoai.video/\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\" data-hveid=\"0\" decode-data-ved=\"1\" data-ved=\"0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwjQwqnV6P2TAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ2gI\">https://hailuoai.video/</a></link-block></response-element></strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em data-path-to-node=\"9,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"31\">(注：海外版独享无阉割的底层模型与极速算力，需自备海外网络节点)</em>。</span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\"><br/></p>",
